<div class="ss-faq">
  <div class="ss-faq__container">
    <h2 class="ss-faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="ss-faq__list">
      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-1" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-1" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>What is a natal chart?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>A natal chart, also known as a birth chart, is a map of the sky at the exact moment you were born. It shows the positions of the Sun, Moon, planets, and other celestial bodies relative to the Earth, and serves as the foundation for your personalized astrology book.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-2" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-2" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>How is this book customized?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>Your book is generated using the precise astronomical data from your birth — date, time, and location. Our algorithms calculate your natal chart and our astrologers craft personalized interpretations for each planetary placement unique to you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-3" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-3" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>Can I order a book as a gift for someone else?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>Absolutely! Many of our customers order Star Story books as gifts. Simply enter the recipient's birth details during the ordering process. You can also add a personal message that will be included in the book.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-4" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-4" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>What if I don't know my exact birth time?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>If you don't know your exact birth time, you can still order a book. We'll use a noon birth time as a default, which provides accurate Sun sign, Mercury, Venus, Mars, Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, Neptune, and Pluto placements. Only the Moon sign and Rising sign may differ.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-5" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-5" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>How accurate does the birth location need to be?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>The city of birth is sufficient for an accurate natal chart calculation. You don't need to know the exact hospital or address — just the city or town where you were born.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-6" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-6" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>What does the book include?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>Your personalized book includes detailed interpretations of your Sun sign, Moon sign, Rising sign, and all planetary placements (Mercury through Pluto), plus your Midheaven and North Node. Each section explains how these cosmic influences shape your personality, relationships, career, and life path.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-7" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-7" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>What size is the book and how many pages does it have?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>The book is 8x8 inches (approximately 20x20 cm) and contains around 90 pages of beautifully designed, full-color content personalized to your birth chart.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-8" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-8" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>How long will it take to receive my book?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>Your book is custom-created within 7 business days of your order. Shipping typically takes an additional 7 business days, so you can expect to receive your book within approximately 14 business days of ordering.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-9" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-9" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>Can I make changes to my order after it's been placed?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>We begin processing orders quickly, so please double-check all birth details before placing your order. If you need to make changes, contact our support team as soon as possible and we'll do our best to accommodate your request.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-faq__item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-10" class="ss-faq__toggle">
        <label for="ss-faq-10" class="ss-faq__question">
          <span>What is your return policy?</span>
          <span class="ss-faq__icon"></span>
        </label>
        <div class="ss-faq__answer">
          <p>Because each book is uniquely created for you, we cannot accept returns for incorrect birth details provided by the customer. However, if there is a printing error or damage during shipping, we will happily replace your book at no additional cost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
.ss-faq {
  background: #e4dcca;
  padding: 40px 20px 61px;
}

.ss-faq__container {
  max-width: 1240px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.ss-faq__title {
  font-family: "Noto Serif", serif;
  color: #1a3050;
  font-size: 32px;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 0 0 32px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.ss-faq__item {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  padding: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ss-faq__toggle {
  display: none;
}

.ss-faq__question {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a3050;
  margin: 0;
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
}

.ss-faq__icon {
  position: relative;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-left: 16px;
}

.ss-faq__icon::before,
.ss-faq__icon::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  background: #1a3050;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.ss-faq__icon::before {
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 16px;
  height: 2px;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.ss-faq__icon::after {
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 2px;
  height: 16px;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.ss-faq__toggle:checked ~ .ss-faq__question .ss-faq__icon::after {
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(90deg);
}

.ss-faq__toggle:checked ~ .ss-faq__question .ss-faq__icon::before {
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(180deg);
}

.ss-faq__answer {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
}

.ss-faq__toggle:checked ~ .ss-faq__answer {
  max-height: 500px;
}

.ss-faq__answer p {
  padding: 0 20px 20px;
  margin: 0;
  font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #555;
}
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "SS - FAQ",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
